name: Reporte de Barrios
query:
select t.name as barrio, t.parent_territory as municipio,
        (select t1.parent_territory from `tabTerritory` t1 where t1.name=t.parent_territory) as departamento,
        t.tipo_territorio, br.parent as ruta
from `tabTerritory` t left join `tabBarrios y Rutas` br on t.name=br.barrios
where t.tipo_territorio='Barrio'
